attributes.review: This app was recommended to my by our president, Mr.Orange. I figured why not try it out. He didnt make america great the first four years he was elected but maybe if we give him four more he can finally do what he said he would back in 2016. After waiting a month fir it to download i owned the app to see a nazi on my screen. I screamed and threw my phone shattering the screen. I got my new phone and re-downloaded the app and as soon as i opened it my head started aching and my ears started ringing and i started having a seizure. Once i got to the doctor they ran a billion tests and told me i had brain cancer, and it was terminal. They said they will do further research and that i should look into my families history to see if its genetic. As i opened google on my phone i got a notification from the trump app saying that i should come reserve a ticket to his next rally. I had gotten tickets to his last rally but sadly i couldn't go because i had to walk my fish. As i open the app the room starts spinning and i loose my vision. I quickly turn off my phone and everything goes back to normal. I book an appointment and tell the doctor both time that i had medical problems i was opening the trump app. He instantly says,” i know your problem, you have too much of the faccistpig and racism hormone its causing you brain cancer, delete the app and it should go away shortly.” I deleted the app and the brain cancer went away, tumor and all. I am currently working on a lawsuit just like stormy Daniels, hoping to get some cash from my trauma caused by this app.Do NOT DOWNLOAD THIS APP!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
attributes.title: This app gave me brain cancer.
